{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/multiversx/mx-sdk-rs/pulls/936", "id": 1197528645, "node_id": "PR_kwDODdCLlc5HYNZF", "html_url": "https://github.com/multiversx/mx-sdk-rs/pull/936", "diff_url": "https://github.com/multiversx/mx-sdk-rs/pull/936.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/multiversx/mx-sdk-rs/pull/936.patch", "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/multiversx/mx-sdk-rs/issues/936", "number": 936, "state": "closed", "locked": false, "title": "SC upgrade tool", "user": {"login": "andrei-marinica", "id": 26074099, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI2MDc0MDk5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26074099?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica", "html_url": "https://github.com/andrei-marinica", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andrei-marinica/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "body": "Smart contract upgrade tool that can upgrade contracts up to version 0.39.0 (for now).\r\n\r\nIt is easy to expand with code for new versions. It also has a default implementation that simply bumps versions in the crate configs.\r\n\r\nThe upgrade tool is part of the meta crate, which can now also be called as a standalone application. \r\n\r\nAlso refactored the meta crate CLI arguments using `clap`. Aside from the more concise implementation, we also have the following help:\r\n\r\n```\r\nMultiversX smart contract meta-programming tools and build system\r\n\r\nUsage: sc-meta [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  build      Builds contract(s) for deploy on the blockchain.\r\n  build-dbg  Builds contract(s) with symbols and WAT.\r\n  twiggy     Builds contract(s) and generate twiggy reports.\r\n  clean      Clean the Rust project and the output folder.\r\n  snippets   Generates a snippets project, based on the contract ABI.\r\n  upgrade    Upgrades a contract to the latest version. Multiple contract crates are allowed.\r\n  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n      --no-abi-git-version  Skips loading the Git version into the ABI\r\n  -h, --help                Print help\r\n  -V, --version             Print version\r\n\r\n\r\nThe MultiversX smart contract Meta crate can be used in two ways:\r\n    A. Import it into a contract's specific meta-crate. \r\n       There it will receive access to the contract ABI generator. \r\n       Based on that it is able to build the contract and apply various tools.\r\n       This part also contains the multi-contract config infrastructure.\r\n\r\n    B. Use it as a standalone tool.\r\n       It can be used to automatically upgrade contracts from one version to the next.\r\n```\r\n\r\nRunning the upgrade tool produces a colorful output:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-01-17 18-06-20](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/26074099/212954159-d4f2f307-2a32-4c55-8e99-297c38b3273c.png)\r\n", "created_at": "2023-01-14T11:45:17Z", "updated_at": "2023-01-18T16:37:20Z", "closed_at": "2023-01-18T16:37:16Z", "merged_at": "2023-01-18T16:37:16Z", "merge_commit_sha": "84e2bd04567ffdd5e52179b596b2fc22f55c111b", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/multiversx/mx-sdk-rs/pulls/936/commits",